Package: HoardR
Title: Cache and Save R Objects, Tables, and Figures
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Basilin", "Benson", , "bbenson@benaroyaresearch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A unified toolkit for caching and saving R objects, tables, and 
    figures. Provides smart caching that loads from disk if available, otherwise 
    computes and saves. Supports RDS for complex objects, CSV/TSV for flat 
    tables, and multiple figure formats via ggplot2.
